data.description: 2022 constructed home in Bent Pine Preserve golf community. One of the few models with dual-zone a/c. Upgrades include vaulted and coffered ceilings, surround sound, security system, water conditioner w/ reverse osmosis, and wine bar. Gourmet kitchen has double ovens, exhaust hood, waterfall island, and large pantry. Tile flooring, crown molding, impact glass, and quartz counter tops throughout. Golf or social membership with seasonal reciprocals available for additional cost. Community tennis courts, bike trails, and 24-hour gated and guarded security. Amazing lake view.
